_sText: This is my first real map I have made. I have some experience with hammer, mostly juts messing around with physics, and attempting to make maps. Please don't be too harsh. There are three levels, one secret button on each level. If you press the three secret buttons you will unlock the secret minigame ending. There are also two secret grenades spread throughout the level. Enjoy! Please give me feedback as I am planning on adding on to this.
